Package: HPZoneAPI
Type: Package
Title: HPZone API Interface in R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dijkstra", "Aart", email="a.dijkstra@ggdnog.nl", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph")) 
Maintainer: Aart Dijkstra <a.dijkstra@ggdnog.nl>
Description: Package that simplifies the use of HPZone's API. Most of the annoying and labor-intensive parts of the interface are handled by wrapper functions.
